      "E₁ / √2"
    ],
    [
      "√2 E₁"
    ],
    [
      "2E₁"
    ],
    [
      "E₁ / 2"
    ]
  ],
  "correctAnswer": 1,
  "explanation": [
    "Mean Kinetic Energy ∝ Temperature (in Kelvin).",
    "T₁ = 27 + 273 = 300 K.",
    "T₂ = 327 + 273 = 600 K.",
    "E₂/E₁ = T₂/T₁ = 600/300 = 2.",
    "E₂ = 2E₁.",
